g.text: Network connectivity, Remote control & Management are requested across the vertical, partners and end-users
POE Amplifiers, a notable focus by reducing cabling costs and increasing the scalabilityNetwork capable Amplifiers, can be controlled from a centralized or even remote location

Live & Touring mixers must be remotely enabled- Sound engineers want to be able to control the mixer using a tablet or smartphone from a cross a room or venue- Remote workflows involve maintenance, distance mixing or sending the content from one location to another
Dante, a crucial feature with interoperability of devices in installed commercial, live and touring.
Biamp, QSC and Symetrix lead the market by providing multi-feature, configurable and expanding DSP
